## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available literature and studies up to October 2023. Some sources may not have the most current data, and the rapidly evolving nature of social media platforms means that new trends and impacts may not be fully captured. Additionally, individual differences in social media usage and personal sleep habits can vary widely, making it challenging to generalize findings across all demographics.

